# JWT Secret (Optional - used for server-side JWT verification if needed)
# How to get it:
# 1. Go to your Supabase Dashboard: https://supabase.com/dashboard
# 2. Select your project
# 3. Go to Settings (gear icon in sidebar)
# 4. Click on "API" in the settings menu (or look for "API Keys")
# 5. Scroll down to find "JWT Settings" or "JWT Secret" section
# 6. The JWT Secret will be a long base64 string (64+ characters)
# 7. Click "Reveal" or "Copy" to get your JWT secret
# Only needed if you're doing custom JWT verification on the server
SUPABASE_JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret_here

